(1, 'oelpqy-gdrnqv-hixzpb-eofban-bhqyvc', 1, 'Welcome To Email Subscribers', '<strong style=\"color: #990000\">What can you achieve using Email Subscribers?</strong><p>Add subscription forms on website, send HTML newsletters. You can also Import or Export subscribers from any list to Email Subscribers.</p> <strong style=\"color: #990000\">Plugin Features</strong><ol> <li>Send notification emails to subscribers when new blog posts are published.</li> <li>Subscribe form available with 3 options to setup.</li> <li>Double Opt-In and Single Opt-In support.</li> <li>Email notification to admin when a new user signs up (Optional).</li> <li>Automatic welcome email to subscriber.</li> <li>Auto add unsubscribe link in the email.</li> <li>Import/Export subscriber emails to migrate to any lists.</li> <li>Default WordPress editor to create emails.</li> </ol> <strong>Thanks & Regards,</strong><br/>Admin<br/>', 2, 'Sent', '2021-08-29 03:19:20', '2021-08-29 03:19:30', NULL, '2021-08-29 03:19:18', '2021-08-29 03:19:18'),
