(504, 1, '2021-10-17 07:27:57', '2021-10-17 00:27:57', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">In the past, there was a kingdom in West Kalimantan. The King had 7 little girls. The queen had actually passed away. The king did not intend to remarry.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The seven daughters were beautiful. Nevertheless, the youngest little girl was one of the most stunning. She was likewise the kindest. She commonly helped other individuals. Her sisters were significantly different. They were lazy. They additionally had attitude problem. They were cruel to individuals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The king learnt about his daughters practices. He typically advise his older child to practices. He commonly advise his older little girls to behave like the youngest little girl. Regretfully, they never heard the king’s advice. They hated their youngest sibling due to the fact that the king commonly praised her excellent behavior.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The older children commonly did horrible points to the youngest child. They commonly struck her. She was very depressing. She usually cried. She might not inform it to her daddy since her older siblings constantly intimidated her. They would certainly strike her also harder if she informed their daddy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">One day, the king asked all her daughters to meet him.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">” I’m mosting likely to the bordering kingdom. I’ll opt for numerous months. While I’m gone, my youngest daughter will rule the kingdom. Do you comprehend?” asked the king.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\"><em>” Yes, we do, Papa, “claimed all the little girls.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The older children were upset. They very upset regarding their youngest sibling was asked to rule the kingdom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">After the king left, they prepared something negative. They wished to remove their youngest sister. They pretended to be wonderful to her. The youngest child enjoyed. Lastly, her older siblings behaved to her.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The older sisters asked her to go fishing. They asked to head to Gua Batu or a stone cave. There was a river streaming inside the cavern. And there were a great deal of fish because river.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The youngest child was so delighted when they ultimately reached the cave. She did not know that her siblings were mosting likely to do something negative to her.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">” Rush, let’s go inside the cave. You could discover a lot of fish inside the cavern,” said the oldest daughter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">The youngest was so excited. As she went inside the cavern, she did not know that her sis remained outside the cavern. They continued asking her to go inside the cave.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">She kept walking till she was shed! She was calling out all her sis, however they did not respond. She after that recognized that her siblings did not want her to rule the kingdom anymore.<br>She was extremely sad. She sobbed. Instantly an old man came. He was a holy man. He was practicing meditation in the cave. She changed her tears right into eggs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">” Don’t fret, I could assist you. You can go back to the kingdom yet you need to change into a bird. I call you Ruai Bird. Afterwards, Brood these eggs. After they hatch, the birds will accompany you,” stated the old man.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size\">She agreed. Slowly she became a stunning bird. And also nevertheless the eggs were hatched, they went back to the kingdom. They all stayed at the tree near the kingdom. They all saw exactly how the king penalized the older sis</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Legend of Ruai Bird', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '320-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-1